00 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">WARM</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">WARM RED</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 185</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">RED (PMS 185)</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 192</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">RED (PMS 192)</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 201</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">MAROON</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">RED</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">RUBINE RED</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 221</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">BURGUNDY</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PANTONE PURPLE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">PURPLE</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PANTONE VIOLET</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">VIOLET</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">REFLEX</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">REFLEX BLUE</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 300</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">BLUE (PMS 300)</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PROCESS BLUE</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 320</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">TEAL</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 356</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">GREEN</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 430</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">GREY</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 470</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">BROWN</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 485</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">RED (PMS 485)</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 873</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">GOLD</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 877</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">SILVER</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 1205 @30%</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">IVORY</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/1/C/1CB5D728215DCA3E405067BA50969F67.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">PMS 201</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pantone 201 Red</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><div class=\"mb-2\"><img src=\"https://s3.distributorcentral.com/uploads/F/6/F6272A4927BE0036563348FA77497804.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"max-h-28 max-w-[180px] rounded border border-neutral-200 object-contain\" loading=\"lazy\" /></div><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9001</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Pantone Color Match</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Printed to match Coated Pantone Color Bridge book.</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$50.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Copy Change Pads</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Select the number of additional changes and use the Choices text box to type in instructions. If you have different copy for the same product, you may group the copy changes on the same order. \r\n\r\n&lt;strong&gt;NOTE:&lt;/strong&gt; There is only 1 copy change charge no matter how many colors change if printing is in full color (four color process). Published minimum quantities for all products apply for copy changes. Copy Changes are limited to changing 6 lines of copy, a photo and a logo. In addition, the items must all have a common background or main layout that does not change.\r\n\r\n&lt;i&gt;Please Note: Once an order is submitted to factory, copy changes cannot be added.&lt;/i&gt;\r\n&lt;hr&gt;</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">9006PAD</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Note Pad Proof Options</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9ONLINE</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Internet Color Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Online Proofing is to show you color and/or color breaks, but IS NOT an exact color matching proofing system. Output from laser printers, ink-jet printers or what you view on your computer monitor cannot be matched. These methods are subjective and may not accurately represent your final printed product.</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">9002</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Production Proof</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Actual printed &amp; laminated product proofs. Pre-Production Proofs for Wall Calendar/Booklet Pre-Production Proof are printed on a digital press. The final product may be printed on a conventional press, therefore, a 5% difference in color, contrast and saturation may occur.&lt;strong&gt;Product proofs are sent via overnight shipping at customer's expense.  If you do not want your proofs expedited, please contact Customer Service.  Printed product proofs &amp; shipping are FREE OF CHARGE on orders of $6,250(G) or more.   Pantone® color matches are billed at $50(C) per color on all product proofs.&lt;/strong&gt;</p><p class=\"mt-1 text-[12px] font-medium text-neutral-800\">$80.00 each</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Bleed on Scratch Pads - Finish size 8.00&quot; x 10.50&quot; w/bleeds</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Optional bleed on scratch pads. Bleeds are free of  charge, however the finished size of this pad will be 8.00&quot; x 10.50&quot; to accommodate the bleed.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">9BLEED5005</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Chipboard Backer for 8.5x11 Notepad</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Replace 12 pt Backer with 22 mil Chipboard</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">9ChipboardLG</p></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — Scratch Pad / Notepad - 25 Sheets - 8.5x11. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">5005025</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>10 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">250</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}